ūn</i>."]}]},{"name":"Godric","type":"LAST","attribution":"Dictionary of Family Names in Britain and Ireland © University of the West of England 2016","meanings":["English:  see  Goodrich  ."],"variants":[{"name":"Goodrich","meanings":["B. G.: Rich in God."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Godric The Saxon was born in 1035, in England, United Kingdom. He married wife Godric The Saxon before 1060, in Europe. They were the parents of at least 1 son. He died in 1066, in his hometown, at the age of 31."},"et":{"1035–1066":"1035–1066","–Female":"Surnud","1060–Male":"1060–Surnud","about 1060":"umbes 1060","1035":"1035","1066":"1066","before 1060":"enne 1060","1060":"1060","Europe":"Europe","Croxton, Cheshire, England, United Kingdom":"Croxton, Cheshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","England, United Kingdom":"Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1035–1066":"1035–1066","–Female":"Kuollut","1060–Male":"1060–Kuollut","about 1060":"noin 1060","1035":"1035","1066":"1066","before 1060":"ennen vuotta 1060","1060":"1060","Europe":"Europe","Croxton, Cheshire, England, United Kingdom":"Croxton, Cheshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","England, United Kingdom":"Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1035–1066":"1035–1066","–Female":"Décédée","1060–Male":"1060–Décédé","about 1060":"environ 1060","1035":"1035","1066":"1066","before 1060":"avant 1060","1060":"1060","Europe":"Europe","Croxton, Cheshire, England, United Kingdom":"Croxton, Cheshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","England, United Kingdom":"Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Godric The Saxon est né en 1035, à Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Il a épousé wife Godric The Saxon avant 1060, à Europe. Ils ont eu au moins 1 fils. Il est décédé en 1066, dans sa ville natale, à l’âge de 31 ans."},"de":{"1035–1066":"1035–1066","–Female":"Verstorben","1060–Male":"1060–Verstorben","about 1060":"um 1060","1035":"1035","1066":"1066","before 1060":"vor 1060","1060":"1060","Europe":"Europa","Croxton, Cheshire, England, United Kingdom":"Croxton, Cheshire